{"tid":276139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角騷亂】警長稱手因擋磚而受傷 醫療報告指是跌傷","createTime":"2017-06-08T14:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T03:37:05.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0912bcd724ed1e260624a587370405acf6a82811","tid":276139,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"去年大年初二凌晨旺角發生的騷亂，事後多人被控以暴動罪，其中涉及9名男子的案件今續審。案發時為總督察的現任警司陳偉基供稱，其左手當日因擋磚而受傷，但被辯方質疑指其醫療報告是註明他是跌傷，陳表示不知原因。<br />\n<br />\n控方在庭上播放當日的新聞片段，以及中銀的閉路電視片段，看到陳偉基被磚掟中後流血。陳指在拘捕第六被告後現場開始平靜，否則若他及警長黃樂安再中磚會有「更嚴重受傷，死亡都唔出奇」。<br />\n<br />\n而辯方指第六被告陳和祥(71歲)當日是剛步出行人隧道便被制服，被告根本沒有掟磚，惟陳指目擊第六被告有掟磚，之後見警方開始拘捕掟磚者後，便用龜速跑。"},{"pid":"d36e79d64b69aec42cacc27be7fdbf48ec1a4d1a","tid":276139,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6345c3d48672927dd18e2956d091d24a8cac345","tid":276139,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"阿伯你都屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ec7f511afe6d3f9892c9eb4ca65226ddfc2b7e","tid":276139,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91e3c138f08eebe72d23257ba40604ef8d0d3a1","tid":276139,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:47:22.000Z","msg":"地下啲磚唔係磚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9643b0bf4e551f2d350c212b483fc59ee0b27050","tid":276139,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0